Frontend
========

## Required packages
* openssl, openssl-devel
* openvpn
* fail2ban

## Installation checklist
* Enable repos
* Install VM-Containers
* Install OpenVPN
* Setup oneadmin account
* sync oneadmin account to vm-containers
* Setup OpenVPN
* Update service scripts
* Make sure that selinux is turned off
* Update iptables rules using Rocks 
* Make sure that NetworkManager is turned off
* Turn on all related services

## Notes
* Update brctl path in OpenNebula's network script